---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-[#EEF2F8] via-[#F5F8FD] to-[#F8FAFE] py-24">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.15]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, #004ADD 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[#DCEAFD] bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm">
          Support & Info
        </div>
        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold font-display text-[#02275A] leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Find clear, practical answers to the questions members ask most often about membership, classes, accessibility, and day-to-day participation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.45fr_0.85fr] items-start">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F8FAFC] via-white to-[#F5F8FD] p-5 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <div class="mb-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#DCEAFD] bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#004ADD]">
              Member Support
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>What are the main office hours?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                Monday – Friday: 8:00 a.m. – 5:00 p.m.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>How do I become a member?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                You may sign up in person at the main office or via the website. To join online, click the link “Join OLLI-HU”, fill out the form, and pay your dues.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>How can members volunteer?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                Activities are organized and operated by our members. As a democratic membership organization, OLLI at HU depends on the volunteer services of its members. Volunteering brings involvement in the Institute in meaningful and satisfying ways.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>Can members bring a guest to classes or activities?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                OLLI classes and activities are designed for members only. However, members may bring a guest for a one-time visit as a class auditor; the guest may attend as long as they pay the appropriate fee and are approved by OLLI at HU staff.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>Where are classes located?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                Classes are held at the W.O. Lawton Building and various local satellite locations, depending on the schedule for each term.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>Do members need parking passes?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                When attending day and/or overnight trips, a parking pass is required and should be obtained in advance through the appropriate office or event instructions.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>Can accommodations be provided for accessibility needs?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                We are dedicated to making our courses and events accessible to all participants. Please contact us in advance so we can coordinate accommodations that support your participation and comfort.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>What is the inclement weather policy?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                OLLI follows Hampton University’s weather policy. Please check the university’s official weather announcements and any communicated updates before attending in-person classes or events.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>How do I sign up for trips?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                Trip sign-ups are only permitted on the designated sign-up days. We encourage members to mark their calendars and plan accordingly to secure their spot.
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 py-6 text-lg font-semibold font-display text-[#02275A] transition hover:bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <span>What is the refund and credit policy?</span>
                <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xl font-medium text-[#004ADD] shadow-sm transition group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="px-2 pb-6 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700">
                No refunds or credits will be given for local, overnight trips, and movie days. Please review event-specific policies before registering.
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-[#02275A] p-8 text-white shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#93C5FD]">Quick Contact</p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Office hours</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#DDE8FF]">
              Monday – Friday, 8:00 a.m. – 5:00 p.m.
            </p>
            <a href="https://form.jotform.com/240354605024143" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-center text-base font-semibold text-[#02275A] shadow-lg transition hover:bg-[#F3F8FC]">
              Join OLLI-HU
            </a>
          </div>

        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_-25px_rgba(2,39,90,0.25)] sm:p-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#004ADD]">Membership</p>
            <h2 id="membership" class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Annual Membership</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-full bg-[#F5F8FD] px-4 py-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[#02275A]">
            $60 per year
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
          Membership includes all OLLI at Hampton University programs, events, and access to the Institute’s member-led activities. The annual fee is the foundation of the organization’s programming and supports the community experience.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Membership fee benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-lg text-slate-700">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#004ADD]"></span><span>Access to OLLI classes, lectures, and special events.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#004ADD]"></span><span>Participation in member-led activities and social programs.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#004ADD]"></span><span>Eligibility to join the broader Hampton University lifelong learning community.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-[#F5F8FD] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Course fee</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-700">
              Most courses are available for an additional <span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">$60</span> fee, depending on the offering and format.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 border-t border-slate-200 pt-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Examples of membership scenarios</h3>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
              <p><span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Scenario 1:</span> Member joins for the year and attends a single course. Total: <span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">$60 annual membership</span> plus the course fee if applicable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
              <p><span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Scenario 2:</span> Member joins and participates in a full slate of classes and activities throughout the year. Total: <span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">$60 annual membership</span> plus <span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">$60 per course</span> where applicable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
              <p><span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">Scenario 3:</span> Member attends events without enrolling in courses. Total: <span class="font-semibold text-[#02275A]">$60 annual membership</span> only, with no additional course fee.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
